## API Reference

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `title` | `string` | Yes | Primary empty state message. |
| `description` | `string` | No | Supporting text. |
| `icon` | `Snippet` | No | Icon rendered above the title. |
| `commandLine` | `string` | No | Copyable command line rendered with a copy button. |
| `contents` | `Snippet` | No | Custom content such as action buttons. |
| `children` | `Snippet` | No | Fallback custom content when `contents` is not provided. |
| `size` | `"sm" \| "base" \| "lg"` | No | Empty state size. Defaults to `"base"`. |
| `class` | `string` | No | Additional classes. |

The component also accepts standard `HTMLDivElement` attributes.
